{"tid":2506654,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食蒸魚係咪應該要考牌","createTime":"2021-04-27T12:31:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T12:35:09.000Z","uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a822f66af0dfe67ab6abc179ad094b8c7dadd153","tid":2506654,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T12:31:22.000Z","msg":"費事同枱啲傻佬lur骨又唔識，然後妹到成枱都係魚骨同爛魚肉碎，好影響食慾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有啲反魚柒下柒下，然後成條魚達落去啲豉油，或者反到條魚斷開一半<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔想反魚揀起骨，有啲人又整到條魚爛蓉蓉咁，骨同肉撈埋一齊，點能食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd566bc42d10d75f1702bb126db05228c799197","tid":2506654,"uid":222390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T12:35:09.000Z","msg":"魚我食開爭鮮無骨嗰隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}